{"tid":2102664,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"大家估下聽日初選會發生咩特發事件？","createTime":"2020-07-10T15:31:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T11:12:52.000Z","uid":143343,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"7f4734f2fdde0b29880da6b7a5feb6debe995d6f","tid":2102664,"uid":143343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T15:31:14.000Z","msg":"我估應該有一大班人唔記得帶地址證明<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be1e819d09b339e1e2bdd6b59c77f2be6fd8d5de","tid":2102664,"uid":358691,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T15:31:48.000Z","msg":"因為而家有唔少人都唔太sure 投票方法，請盡量用wtsapp, tg, ig, fb 話比身邊嘅人知幾個重點：<br />\n1️⃣. 帶身份證+ 住址證明*（不能為選民紀錄截圖）<br />\n2️⃣. Andriod 用家請事前download<br />\n &lt;普及投票 4.0 mobile app&gt; <br />\n -- Andriod版:<a href=\"https://is.gd/tH1bbk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fis.gd%2FtH1bbk&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwumuSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=10b60678\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://is.gd/tH1bbk</a> <br />\n<br />\n Apple 朋友❗唔使app, 到時scan Qr web投❗<br />\nApple 唔使app~<br />\nApple 唔使app~<br />\nApple 唔使app~<br />\n #重要的事說三次<br />\n <br />\n3️⃣ 因為7/10唔少地方集體被業主通知唔可以做票站，所以請各位務必📣喺出發前check check 最update 票站地址， 以免摸門釘📣 <a href=\"https://qrgo.page.link/uVuQi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqrgo.page.link%2FuVuQi&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwumuSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=3fa1442a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://qrgo.page.link/uVuQi</a><br />\n（更新自7/10, 20：33）<br />\n<br />\n最後，記得星期六日去投票!<br />\n<br />\n----------<br />\n*可接受的住址證明:(電子版/相/screen cap/實物均可）<br />\n<br />\na. 由下列機構一年內發出的文件:<br />\n1. 水∕電∕煤∕中央石油氣供應商(不包括中央石油氣營運商)收費單或發票<br />\n2. 固網電話∕流動電話∕收費電視∕互聯網收費單<br />\n3. 銀行、持牌放債人、保險公司或強積金核准受託公司發出之結單或通知書<br />\n4. 政府部門或司法機構(法庭)發出之文件<br />\n例如:繳稅通知書、徵收差餉及∕或地租通知書、償還學生貸款通知書<br />\n5. 本地大學或可頒授學位的高等教育院校發出的文件或收費單<br />\n6. 由稅務局加蓋釐印的有效租約<br />\n7. 下列公營機構發出的收費單、通知書或其他文件<br />\n&bull; 醫院管理局<br />\n&bull; 香港房屋委員會<br />\n&bull; 香港房屋協會<br />\n&bull; 香港考試及評核局<br />\n8. 下列機構發出的收費單、通知書或其他文件<br />\n&bull; 快易通(Autotoll)<br />\n&bull; 在港供應車輛用汽油∕柴油∕石油氣公司<br />\n&bull; 指定駕駛學校(包括:香港駕駛學院及觀塘駕駛學院) &bull; 國際慈善機構(例如:聯合國兒童基金會)<br />\n&bull; 本地註冊的慈善機構(例如:香港公益金)<br />\n<br />\n或<br />\n9. 有全名的屋苑住戶證<br />\n10. 有屋苑或屋村全名的居民協會會員證"},{"pid":"3e11204c85524ba08317d458ab600992175e77f1","tid":2102664,"uid":143343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T15:32:02.000Z","msg":"仲有可能搵唔到自己屋企附近票站位置都大機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48957145662c65bd9d06fe45386f0abd49e63b97","tid":2102664,"uid":231522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T15:32:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />直接拉曬翻去"},{"pid":"86be247e5ac87e7dc0d169b75d9c91d73646b575","tid":2102664,"uid":143343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48957145662c65bd9d06fe45386f0abd49e63b97","tid":2102664,"uid":231522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T15:32:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />直接拉曬翻去"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T15:33:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15302f3b9a715546c95b332c85e22e000c2e8123","tid":2102664,"uid":143343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T15:36:32.000Z","msg":"藍屍入場投黃碧雲"},{"pid":"f742c22ab50bd95a751d92b8b2975d2df6af24df","tid":2102664,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T16:07:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed6aaaca4a805bdb393a469badf266669f674641","tid":2102664,"uid":78447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T16:14:29.000Z","msg":"使唔使去返自己嗰區嘅票站？<br />\n例如我本身係新界西，但就